"      Overview of tremor",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?19/17/19737?source=see_link\">",
"      Pharmacologic treatment of essential tremor",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/4/28741?source=see_link\">",
"      Surgical treatment of essential tremor",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
